buckets.name: con
buckets.comments:
Entity can either be private or public.

When one Entity follows other Entity . it first check the status that if profile of the other Entity is public or private. 
1. If it is public an edge name 'follows' is directed from one Entity to other.

2. If it is private then an edge named request is directed from one Entity to other and when the other Entity accept the follows request the an edge named follows will be created removing request edge. And if the request is rejected the request edge will be deleted.
